0.1.name: wordpress/linkedin-hresume
0.1.description:
This plugin is no longer in active development and may be broken. If you are interested in taking over development, please post a note in the forum.

LinkedIn hResume for Wordpress grabs the hResume microformat block from your LinkedIn public profile page allowing you to add it to any Wordpress page and apply your own styles to it.
